    public static final class DynamicMessage.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.AbstractMessage.Builder<DynamicMessage.Builder>
implements ProtoInterfaces.IBuilder2
    A DynamicMessage.Builder wrapping the original protobuf DynamicMessage.Builder and mirroring all relevant GeneratedMessage.Builder functionality, including hierarchical builders, insertion of repeated fields, etc.
    Author:
    protobufel@gmail.com David Tesler
    See Also:
    DynamicMessage.Builder, GeneratedMessage.Builder
